@ijuma I have basically only two (hopefully simple) questions:
* there is no obvious value in the arguments with which the header count should be reconciled; can you please advise what should that be? Shall the number of headers also be compared to the number of validated records?
* please confirm that I have correctly understood, that you'd prefer object oriented approach to the `countOrNull` implementation - implement it in the whole inheritance hierarchy and have return `null` wherever it does not make sense
